1
00:00:35,970 --> 00:00:38,890
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,890 --> 00:00:41,180
=Episode 4=

3
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:45,875
Candied hawthorns!

4
00:00:45,875 --> 00:00:47,583
Do I look strange dressed like this?

5
00:00:47,708 --> 00:00:48,666
You look beautiful.

6
00:00:51,458 --> 00:00:52,125
When people go on dates,

7
00:00:53,208 --> 00:00:54,125
do they all dress like this?

8
00:00:57,833 --> 00:00:58,583
That's the rule.

9
00:01:01,166 --> 00:01:02,625
Is tapping my nose a rule too?

10
00:01:04,083 --> 00:01:04,750
More or less.

11
00:01:07,166 --> 00:01:08,291
The capital truly lives up to its name.

12
00:01:09,041 --> 00:01:10,125
So lively,

13
00:01:10,541 --> 00:01:11,458
so magnificent.

14
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:14,125
This place is my private hideaway.

15
00:01:14,750 --> 00:01:15,750
Even Shizhen and Zhihe

16
00:01:15,958 --> 00:01:16,916
don't know about it.

17
00:01:19,458 --> 00:01:21,625
So, are you pleased with today?

18
00:01:22,291 --> 00:01:23,375
I'm here to repay a favor.

19
00:01:23,833 --> 00:01:24,625
As long as you're pleased.

20
00:01:25,583 --> 00:01:26,375
Just now,

21
00:01:27,625 --> 00:01:29,541
did you feel the ground shake?

22
00:01:31,125 --> 00:01:31,791
No.

23
00:01:32,875 --> 00:01:33,791
Then why

24
00:01:34,458 --> 00:01:35,666
did my heart just tremble?

25
00:01:38,083 --> 00:01:39,666
Tremble? What do you mean?

26
00:01:44,458 --> 00:01:45,708
Because you're beautiful.

27
00:01:46,458 --> 00:01:47,041
So?

28
00:01:49,541 --> 00:01:50,291
So...

29
00:01:52,541 --> 00:01:53,666
They stole my money!

30
00:01:53,958 --> 00:01:54,625
Thieves!

31
00:01:54,625 --> 00:01:55,166
Catch them!

32
00:01:55,166 --> 00:01:55,541
Move!

33
00:01:55,541 --> 00:01:56,083
Catch the thieves!

34
00:01:57,458 --> 00:01:58,375
He stole my money!

35
00:01:58,875 --> 00:02:00,208
Catch the thieves!

36
00:02:01,458 --> 00:02:03,416
Someone help! Catch the thieves!

37
00:02:03,875 --> 00:02:04,791
It's them!

38
00:02:04,916 --> 00:02:05,791
You're dead.

39
00:02:21,083 --> 00:02:21,625
Go.

40
00:02:21,958 --> 00:02:23,500
- Unbelievable.
- Yeah.

41
00:02:26,890 --> 00:02:31,680
♪In a fleeting moment♪

42
00:02:33,270 --> 00:02:37,600
♪Whose face crosses my mind♪

43
00:02:39,270 --> 00:02:44,270
♪Whose name is it♪

44
00:02:45,470 --> 00:02:49,770
♪I whisper in my heart♪

45
00:02:50,220 --> 00:02:57,020
♪Yet in the crowd, we brush past♪

46
00:02:57,770 --> 00:03:04,220
♪Afraid memories will fade like dreams♪

47
00:03:04,220 --> 00:03:08,060
♪This longing I cannot say♪

48
00:03:08,060 --> 00:03:13,310
♪I wish you could hear♪

49
00:03:13,333 --> 00:03:14,333
Oh my god.

50
00:03:19,708 --> 00:03:20,416
What are you looking at?

51
00:03:23,541 --> 00:03:24,250
Let's go.

52
00:03:24,833 --> 00:03:27,333
You just dated, and now you're training?

53
00:03:29,083 --> 00:03:30,583
The end-of-month assessment is coming.

54
00:03:32,916 --> 00:03:34,833
You bought a few dresses,

55
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:35,875
had a few bites,

56
00:03:36,458 --> 00:03:37,833
then ran off to catch thieves,

57
00:03:38,208 --> 00:03:39,166
and came right back?

58
00:03:39,500 --> 00:03:41,875
That was your first date?

59
00:03:43,500 --> 00:03:45,833
But he paid for the clothes and meal.

60
00:03:46,291 --> 00:03:47,041
Well,

61
00:03:47,666 --> 00:03:49,500
did he say anything

62
00:03:49,708 --> 00:03:51,208
sweet and flirty?

63
00:03:51,875 --> 00:03:54,291
Words can be sweet and flirty?

64
00:03:56,291 --> 00:03:56,958
Forget it.

65
00:03:58,083 --> 00:03:58,958
Anyway,

66
00:03:59,375 --> 00:04:01,416
I repaid him for getting me
into the Bureau.

67
00:04:01,541 --> 00:04:02,750
Now we're even.

68
00:04:03,083 --> 00:04:04,000
Bingfan,

69
00:04:04,583 --> 00:04:06,791
are you putting on an act,

70
00:04:07,041 --> 00:04:08,333
or do you really not get it?

71
00:04:09,750 --> 00:04:10,916
Get what, Hua?

72
00:04:11,166 --> 00:04:12,250
This has nothing to do with you.

73
00:04:12,416 --> 00:04:13,541
Go play somewhere, kid.

74
00:04:13,958 --> 00:04:15,291
I'm not a kid anymore.

75
00:04:16,375 --> 00:04:17,875
Instead of bickering,

76
00:04:18,041 --> 00:04:19,000
you should think about

77
00:04:19,166 --> 00:04:21,375
what we'll do about the assessment.

78
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:22,875
I'm doomed.

79
00:04:23,875 --> 00:04:25,500
In the 28th year of the current reign,

80
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:27,833
Captain Shen Lian of Northern Bureau

81
00:04:28,375 --> 00:04:29,708
was ordered to protect

82
00:04:29,708 --> 00:04:31,791
(Unclosed Cases)
Xu Wenchang, a key witness

83
00:04:31,791 --> 00:04:33,833
in Prince Luo's treason case,
into Huguang.

84
00:04:34,375 --> 00:04:35,625
However, during the escort,

85
00:04:35,958 --> 00:04:37,791
due to Shen Lian's negligence,

86
00:04:39,333 --> 00:04:42,458
Xu Wenchang
and his family were attacked.

87
00:04:46,208 --> 00:04:47,041
That's nonsense.

88
00:04:47,708 --> 00:04:49,208
Silence. This is the Archives.

89
00:04:56,458 --> 00:04:57,083
Archivist Li.

90
00:04:57,750 --> 00:04:59,666
(Case File: Prince Luo's Treason)
May I borrow this case file?

91
00:05:06,333 --> 00:05:07,041
Are you all right?

92
00:05:09,520 --> 00:05:10,930
(Prince Luo's Treason Case)

93
00:05:11,333 --> 00:05:12,333
Prince Luo's treason case?

94
00:05:13,916 --> 00:05:18,125
This case shook
both the court and the country.

95
00:05:18,666 --> 00:05:20,000
It was one of Northern Bureau's

96
00:05:20,291 --> 00:05:23,083
greatest failures of the past ten years.

97
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:24,333
Why?

98
00:05:24,333 --> 00:05:27,833
Shen Lian couldn't guard
the key witness,

99
00:05:27,833 --> 00:05:29,208
which led to the witness's death.

100
00:05:29,458 --> 00:05:31,083
He lost his own life far from home,

101
00:05:31,375 --> 00:05:34,541
and Prince Luo's case came to nothing.

102
00:05:34,875 --> 00:05:37,333
The Northern Bureau
became a laughingstock.

103
00:05:37,791 --> 00:05:39,791
And the Southern Bureau
mocked it for ages.

104
00:05:40,041 --> 00:05:41,125
At the time, Shen Lian

105
00:05:41,708 --> 00:05:43,291
was escorting the witness
to the capital.

106
00:05:44,041 --> 00:05:45,666
But in Huguang,

107
00:05:46,458 --> 00:05:48,083
they were ambushed by assassins.

108
00:05:48,083 --> 00:05:50,291
Even Leng Xin, the top assassin,
was there.

109
00:05:50,625 --> 00:05:52,458
With no allies and no reinforcements,

110
00:05:53,166 --> 00:05:54,500
Shen had to fight to the death.

111
00:05:54,500 --> 00:05:56,125
In the end, he died
under Leng Xin's blade.

112
00:05:56,583 --> 00:05:57,833
He was a hero of Northern Bureau.

113
00:05:58,208 --> 00:05:59,750
How can you call that a failure?

114
00:06:00,500 --> 00:06:01,625
You're awfully upset.

115
00:06:03,583 --> 00:06:05,291
What was Shen Lian to you?

116
00:06:09,500 --> 00:06:10,125
No one.

117
00:06:10,833 --> 00:06:11,708
I just find it unjust.

118
00:06:11,708 --> 00:06:12,958
Why?

119
00:06:12,958 --> 00:06:14,916
Because this file is full of holes.

120
00:06:15,333 --> 00:06:15,833
Tell me.

121
00:06:16,333 --> 00:06:18,625
Shen was escorting the witness
to the capital.

122
00:06:18,875 --> 00:06:20,375
Why would he reveal his own route?

123
00:06:20,750 --> 00:06:21,333
And,

124
00:06:21,833 --> 00:06:23,875
if Xu Wenchang was such
an important witness,

125
00:06:24,250 --> 00:06:25,541
why was no one sent to receive him?

126
00:06:26,375 --> 00:06:28,291
Jinyiwei relay stations
are highly confidential.

127
00:06:28,375 --> 00:06:29,583
How could outsiders know?

128
00:06:29,750 --> 00:06:31,833
And who hired Leng Xin,

129
00:06:31,833 --> 00:06:33,166
the greatest assassin in the land?

130
00:06:33,791 --> 00:06:35,291
Are we ignoring all these questions?

131
00:06:35,416 --> 00:06:36,583
Now that a hero is dead,

132
00:06:36,583 --> 00:06:37,833
people still smear his name.

133
00:06:38,208 --> 00:06:39,083
How is that justice?

134
00:06:40,083 --> 00:06:40,875
Yes.

135
00:06:41,833 --> 00:06:43,416
You do have a point.

136
00:06:45,208 --> 00:06:46,041
But

137
00:06:46,375 --> 00:06:48,458
Northern Bureau isn't stupid.

138
00:06:48,458 --> 00:06:50,333
If this case was buried,

139
00:06:51,166 --> 00:06:51,958
it means

140
00:06:52,500 --> 00:06:53,541
there's more to it.

141
00:06:53,875 --> 00:06:54,666
What more?

142
00:06:54,833 --> 00:06:55,916
How would I know?

143
00:06:56,291 --> 00:06:57,750
I don't work for Northern Bureau.

144
00:06:59,333 --> 00:07:00,500
But I'll tell you this.

145
00:07:00,708 --> 00:07:03,916
The files won't have the truth.

146
00:07:05,291 --> 00:07:06,458
If you want the truth,

147
00:07:07,416 --> 00:07:08,750
you need to get posted

148
00:07:09,208 --> 00:07:13,375
and access the classified archives.

149
00:07:20,250 --> 00:07:21,750
(I can't waste my time here
washing dishes.)

150
00:07:23,500 --> 00:07:25,291
(I need to pay Chang Beiming back,)

151
00:07:25,916 --> 00:07:27,333
(kill Leng Xin,)

152
00:07:27,583 --> 00:07:28,583
(find the traitor,)

153
00:07:29,416 --> 00:07:30,708
(and avenge my father.)

154
00:07:32,875 --> 00:07:33,791
Hey, friend.

155
00:07:34,125 --> 00:07:35,291
I want to buy some information.

156
00:07:35,500 --> 00:07:36,291
What information?

157
00:07:36,750 --> 00:07:37,958
Information on the bounty list.

158
00:07:39,166 --> 00:07:40,916
That kind of information isn't cheap.

159
00:07:42,583 --> 00:07:44,000
Ranked ninth on the bounty list,

160
00:07:44,250 --> 00:07:45,291
Qiankun Rat,

161
00:07:45,541 --> 00:07:48,166
also known as Liu Sankong,
will appear near the capital.

162
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:51,791
Liu Sankong, the Qiankun Rat.

163
00:07:57,166 --> 00:07:58,916
Liu Sankong, the Qiankun Rat.

164
00:07:59,291 --> 00:08:01,000
(Liu Sankong, No. 9 on the Bounty List)
Robbery, burglary, assault,

165
00:08:01,875 --> 00:08:03,583
and 38 lives on your hands.

166
00:08:04,041 --> 00:08:05,541
Ranked ninth on the bounty list.

167
00:08:06,375 --> 00:08:07,375
Reward is two thousand taels.

168
00:08:07,666 --> 00:08:08,458
Dead or alive.

169
00:08:09,750 --> 00:08:10,875
You're the legendary

170
00:08:11,583 --> 00:08:12,333
number one

171
00:08:12,333 --> 00:08:13,250
female bounty hunter?

172
00:08:17,166 --> 00:08:17,833
Take the goods.

173
00:08:17,833 --> 00:08:18,583
Let me go.

174
00:08:18,833 --> 00:08:19,750
I can bring you in

175
00:08:20,083 --> 00:08:21,416
and still collect the bounty.

176
00:08:21,416 --> 00:08:22,416
In your dreams.

177
00:08:22,708 --> 00:08:23,541
If I'm dead either way,

178
00:08:23,666 --> 00:08:25,375
you're not cashing in on my head.

179
00:08:40,125 --> 00:08:41,500
(Chong'er Pavilion)
That was reckless.

180
00:08:41,500 --> 00:08:42,833
Going after Liu Sankong alone?

181
00:08:42,833 --> 00:08:43,916
What were you thinking?

182
00:08:43,916 --> 00:08:45,291
Do you know why he's ranked

183
00:08:45,291 --> 00:08:46,375
in the top ten?

184
00:08:46,375 --> 00:08:47,875
Because he's ruthless.

185
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,541
I wanted to pay you back sooner.

186
00:08:51,208 --> 00:08:52,416
Who asked you to pay me back?

187
00:08:52,416 --> 00:08:54,000
Who said I was in a hurry?

188
00:08:54,833 --> 00:08:56,375
If you ever do something dangerous again

189
00:08:56,375 --> 00:08:57,333
because of this debt,

190
00:08:57,333 --> 00:08:58,541
or because you want to pay me back,

191
00:08:58,541 --> 00:08:59,500
I'm telling you,

192
00:09:01,041 --> 00:09:03,333
I'll charge you triple interest.

193
00:09:04,125 --> 00:09:05,541
All right, Young Master Chang.

194
00:09:07,666 --> 00:09:08,875
I'm coming in.

195
00:09:09,250 --> 00:09:09,916
Come in.

196
00:09:11,041 --> 00:09:12,708
Bingfan, I'll go bring the medicine.

197
00:09:19,375 --> 00:09:20,000
Here's the medicine.

198
00:09:21,583 --> 00:09:22,000
I'll do it.

199
00:09:22,416 --> 00:09:22,833
Here.

200
00:09:26,291 --> 00:09:27,500
Come on. Take your medicine.

201
00:09:28,750 --> 00:09:30,625
I thought I had him.

202
00:09:31,375 --> 00:09:32,916
I didn't think he'd fight desperately.

203
00:09:32,916 --> 00:09:34,791
From today on,

204
00:09:35,208 --> 00:09:36,250
your debt is cleared.

205
00:09:36,583 --> 00:09:38,291
I won't pick fights with you anymore.

206
00:09:38,750 --> 00:09:39,458
And you two.

207
00:09:40,250 --> 00:09:41,416
You don't have to work for me anymore.

208
00:09:42,083 --> 00:09:43,541
Just stop risking your lives, all right?

209
00:09:44,500 --> 00:09:45,625
Debts must be paid.

210
00:09:46,375 --> 00:09:47,500
That's the rule of the martial world.

211
00:09:49,333 --> 00:09:50,375
I'll go capture

212
00:09:50,375 --> 00:09:52,333
Hua Yunfeng, the Ever-Changing Wildcat,

213
00:09:52,958 --> 00:09:53,791
and pay you back.

214
00:09:54,666 --> 00:09:55,500
Hey!

215
00:09:55,666 --> 00:09:57,583
What does Hua Yunfeng have to do
with this?

216
00:09:59,416 --> 00:10:02,000
Hua, who is this Wildcat?

217
00:10:03,625 --> 00:10:07,333
The only woman
in the bounty list's top ten.

218
00:10:08,458 --> 00:10:12,166
Ranked fourth,
the Ever-Changing Wildcat.

219
00:10:12,458 --> 00:10:14,458
That's way too dangerous, Bingfan.

220
00:10:14,750 --> 00:10:16,000
Can you please not go?

221
00:10:16,291 --> 00:10:17,208
It's too dangerous.

222
00:10:18,708 --> 00:10:19,500
Bingfan.

223
00:10:20,125 --> 00:10:20,625
From now on,

224
00:10:21,500 --> 00:10:23,541
if you have the money,

225
00:10:24,208 --> 00:10:25,250
pay me back whenever you want.

226
00:10:25,625 --> 00:10:26,500
And if you don't,

227
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:28,000
I won't bring it up.

228
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:29,875
Just stop taking risks, okay?

229
00:10:34,708 --> 00:10:35,583
Fine.

230
00:10:36,166 --> 00:10:38,750
I'll find another way once I'm healed.

231
00:10:41,916 --> 00:10:43,750
This woman is impossible.

232
00:10:45,125 --> 00:10:45,833
You feed her.

233
00:10:46,333 --> 00:10:46,833
Okay.

234
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:57,416
Young Master.

235
00:10:57,916 --> 00:11:00,041
We recovered Liu Sankong's body.

236
00:11:00,375 --> 00:11:02,125
He drowned
after sustaining severe injuries.

237
00:11:02,291 --> 00:11:03,125
His face was destroyed,

238
00:11:03,125 --> 00:11:04,041
so he can't be identified.

239
00:11:04,416 --> 00:11:05,541
Even if we take him to the authorities,

240
00:11:05,875 --> 00:11:08,041
we probably won't get the bounty.

241
00:11:09,083 --> 00:11:10,125
He got off easy.

242
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:11,458
Take him away and bury him.

243
00:11:12,083 --> 00:11:12,458
Yes.

244
00:11:21,291 --> 00:11:21,958
Bingfan.

245
00:11:22,375 --> 00:11:25,416
What do you think of Chang?

246
00:11:27,208 --> 00:11:29,416
What do you mean?

247
00:11:30,250 --> 00:11:31,500
I mean...

248
00:11:34,833 --> 00:11:37,583
Since it's just us girls here,

249
00:11:37,916 --> 00:11:38,750
let me ask you.

250
00:11:39,250 --> 00:11:42,250
What kind of husband do you want?

251
00:11:42,833 --> 00:11:43,375
I...

252
00:11:44,125 --> 00:11:46,333
I've really never thought about it.

253
00:11:46,708 --> 00:11:48,416
What about Young Master Chang?

254
00:11:49,291 --> 00:11:50,041
(Just now,)

255
00:11:51,250 --> 00:11:53,000
(did you feel the ground shake?)

256
00:11:53,625 --> 00:11:54,166
(No.)

257
00:11:54,208 --> 00:11:55,000
(Then why)

258
00:11:55,750 --> 00:11:57,166
(did my heart just tremble?)

259
00:11:57,430 --> 00:12:02,220
♪In a fleeting moment♪

260
00:12:03,810 --> 00:12:08,140
♪Whose face crosses my mind♪

261
00:12:09,810 --> 00:12:12,770
♪Whose name is it♪

262
00:12:12,791 --> 00:12:13,458
I...

263
00:12:14,583 --> 00:12:16,083
I don't dislike him.

264
00:12:17,625 --> 00:12:19,625
I just don't feel that way about men.

265
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:27,560
♪Yet in the crowd, we brush past♪

266
00:12:28,220 --> 00:12:31,140
♪Only then did I understand fate♪

267
00:12:31,140 --> 00:12:34,350
♪Was hidden in the day we met♪

268
00:12:35,875 --> 00:12:39,267
♪A fate that cannot be severed♪

269
00:12:40,310 --> 00:12:42,560
♪Round and round♪

270
00:12:42,560 --> 00:12:46,890
♪Threads of love bind us together♪

271
00:12:46,970 --> 00:12:51,890
♪Afraid love will fade like smoke♪

272
00:12:53,220 --> 00:12:59,430
♪Afraid memories will vanish like dreams♪

273
00:12:59,430 --> 00:13:03,310
♪This longing I cannot say♪

274
00:13:03,310 --> 00:13:08,390
♪I wish you could hear♪

275
00:13:11,180 --> 00:13:14,140
(Case File: Prince Luo's Treason)

276
00:13:14,791 --> 00:13:16,083
(Awe in Authority, Grace in Virtue)
Last night,

277
00:13:16,083 --> 00:13:17,875
(Awe in Authority, Grace in Virtue)
Scholar Huang Yi of the Hanlin Academy

278
00:13:18,333 --> 00:13:19,833
was assassinated at home.

279
00:13:28,250 --> 00:13:29,625
One strike through the heart.

280
00:13:29,625 --> 00:13:30,625
It was Leng Xin.

281
00:13:30,791 --> 00:13:31,791
Mr. Huang was the top scholar

282
00:13:32,208 --> 00:13:34,000
of the last imperial exam,

283
00:13:34,375 --> 00:13:35,708
a leader among the upright officials.

284
00:13:36,250 --> 00:13:39,416
He was to tutor the Crown Prince,

285
00:13:39,625 --> 00:13:42,458
but was killed at home.

286
00:13:42,833 --> 00:13:45,250
And now Leng Xin is involved.

287
00:13:45,666 --> 00:13:47,083
This is serious.

288
00:13:49,083 --> 00:13:51,791
Could it be connected to that case?

289
00:13:52,208 --> 00:13:52,833
Prince Luo's...

290
00:13:53,791 --> 00:13:54,875
The Cabinet wants this

291
00:13:56,208 --> 00:13:57,000
handled quietly.

292
00:13:57,875 --> 00:13:58,500
Archivist Li,

293
00:13:59,250 --> 00:14:01,416
why are there no files on Leng Xin?

294
00:14:02,250 --> 00:14:05,500
Leng Xin is a top Class-A fugitive.

295
00:14:06,083 --> 00:14:06,916
All his records

296
00:14:06,916 --> 00:14:09,458
are locked in the classified archives.

297
00:14:09,583 --> 00:14:10,541
Not just me.

298
00:14:10,541 --> 00:14:13,125
Even the Commissioner
has no free access.

299
00:14:13,375 --> 00:14:15,083
Even the Commissioner can't?

300
00:14:15,250 --> 00:14:16,791
How long will it take

301
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:18,791
before I can see Leng Xin's file?

302
00:14:19,125 --> 00:14:21,333
Pump Zhang Weimin for information.

303
00:14:21,708 --> 00:14:22,208
Pump him?

304
00:14:22,458 --> 00:14:24,833
That old man loves wine.

305
00:14:24,833 --> 00:14:26,083
Once he's drunk,

306
00:14:27,083 --> 00:14:31,083
he becomes a big blabbermouth.

307
00:14:38,125 --> 00:14:39,625
Young Master Chang knows you enjoy wine.

308
00:14:40,083 --> 00:14:41,291
He prepared this rare vintage

309
00:14:41,791 --> 00:14:44,375
and sent me to bring it for you
to taste.

310
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:51,791
Good. Full-bodied and strong.

311
00:14:53,083 --> 00:14:53,916
Bingfan,

312
00:14:53,916 --> 00:14:56,083
how has training been lately?

313
00:14:56,416 --> 00:14:57,375
How are your lessons?

314
00:14:57,750 --> 00:14:58,625
Thank you for asking.

315
00:14:59,208 --> 00:15:01,250
I'm doing all right in every subject.

316
00:15:02,291 --> 00:15:03,208
It's just...

317
00:15:04,375 --> 00:15:05,041
Just what?

318
00:15:05,833 --> 00:15:07,958
Before joining Northern Bureau,

319
00:15:08,416 --> 00:15:09,458
I wanted nothing more

320
00:15:09,458 --> 00:15:10,291
than to capture Leng Xin,

321
00:15:10,291 --> 00:15:12,250
the top killer on the bounty list.

322
00:15:12,541 --> 00:15:15,583
But why are there so few records

323
00:15:15,916 --> 00:15:16,791
on Leng Xin here?

324
00:15:16,875 --> 00:15:19,250
Actually, here at Northern Bureau,

325
00:15:19,916 --> 00:15:21,833
we have plenty on Leng Xin.

326
00:15:22,500 --> 00:15:25,916
It's all locked
in the classified chamber.

327
00:15:26,708 --> 00:15:28,333
If you want to catch Leng Xin,

328
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:30,500
I'll make you a promise.

329
00:15:30,833 --> 00:15:32,541
If you pass

330
00:15:32,791 --> 00:15:34,208
the end-of-month assessment,

331
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:35,791
I

332
00:15:36,083 --> 00:15:38,375
will grant you special access

333
00:15:38,583 --> 00:15:41,416
to the classified chamber for two hours.

334
00:15:42,583 --> 00:15:46,250
And if you truly capture Leng Xin,

335
00:15:47,166 --> 00:15:50,583
I'll recommend you to His Majesty

336
00:15:52,375 --> 00:15:53,458
for Lu Guokai's post.

337
00:16:12,350 --> 00:16:15,520
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

338
00:16:15,890 --> 00:16:19,270
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

339
00:16:19,520 --> 00:16:22,520
♪My heart drifted lost♪

340
00:16:22,520 --> 00:16:25,930
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

341
00:16:27,020 --> 00:16:30,230
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

342
00:16:30,640 --> 00:16:33,980
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

343
00:16:34,560 --> 00:16:36,770
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

344
00:16:36,770 --> 00:16:40,810
♪I've softly let it go♪

345
00:16:40,810 --> 00:16:44,680
♪The vow you made was true♪

346
00:16:44,680 --> 00:16:48,430
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

347
00:16:48,730 --> 00:16:50,640
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

348
00:16:50,640 --> 00:16:55,180
♪And forget at world's end♪

349
00:16:55,480 --> 00:16:56,980
♪Embracing memory♪

350
00:16:56,980 --> 00:16:59,350
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

351
00:16:59,350 --> 00:17:03,230
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

352
00:17:03,230 --> 00:17:05,560
♪I wish to let it pass♪

353
00:17:05,560 --> 00:17:10,560
♪And run toward this vast life♪

